Error: Error: "FTP Connection Failed" While Using The Pterodactyl Panel For Your Minecraft Server.

Solution: 1. Check that your FTP server is properly configured and running. This can be done using a command-line FTP client or a web-based FTP client. Make sure that you can connect to your FTP server using the same credentials you provided in the Pterodactyl panel.

